# Tick schedule(s) for the slack-deputy dispatcher (cron expressions).
# Copy this file to references/cron and edit it (cron is gitignored).
# Lines starting with # are comments. Each non-comment, non-blank line creates
# one dispatcher cron job.
# Use multiple lines to vary the interval by time of day (e.g. */3 inside a
# window, */20 outside it). Note that overlapping lines can fire on the same
# tick and double-dispatch.
*/3 * * * *
